Nollywood actresss and mother of three, Mercy Johnson Okojie, has shaved off her hair for a new movie she is currently working on. The happily married nollywood star is featuring in a new movie titled “People’s Money“, which just finished shooting recently. Produced by Onyenze Amobi, the movie also stars Atuanya Chigozie, Jude Oteka, Tina Destiny, Ogbu Johnson, Ikechukwu Ojukwu and more. See pictures below ;